      "releaseNotes": "Live Activities now show real-time order updates on your lock screen, as your order goes from our kitchen to your doorstep!\n \nWe’ve also made some new visual optimisations in the menu ordering, reward redemption journeys and recent and favourites, as well as some bug fixes, to make your experience better.",
